       Changes between version 5.3 branch and jgrapÄ¥x branch of Scilab
       ===============================================================

On the merge commit please remove this file and uncomment the 
"AC_JAVA_CHECK_VERSION_PACKAGE([jgraphx]" line on configure.ac with the right
version.

JGraphX:
========

05-JAN-2011: 1.5.1.1

- Moves loadImage, imageCache, PRESERVE_IMAGE_ASPECT to mxBasicCanvas
- Adds embedded images output option using DataURLs in mxSvgCanvas 
- Supports image flipping in all image shapes and canvases
- Adds mxConstants.STYLE_IMAGE_FLIPH/FLIPV for image

20-DEC-2010: 1.5.1.0

- Fixes possible NPE in mxGraph.getCell-/EdgeValidationError
- Fixes moving of vertices after mxGraphComponent.setTransferHandler
- Uses smooth image scaling by default in mxGraphics2DCanvas.drawImage
- Adds mxGraphics2DCanvas.IMAGE_SCALING switch
- Adds mxGd-, mxGdi-, mxGraphics2DCanvas.PRESERVE_IMAGE_ASPECT switch
- Fixes mxGd-, mxGdi-, mxGraphics2DCanvas.drawImage to preserve image aspects
- Fixes mxSwimlaneManager to use parent swimlane orientation
- Adds mxSwimlaneManager.isCellHorizontal, hasSiblings

08-DEC-2010: 1.5.0.2

- Adds mxRectangle.setRect
- Adds mxPanningHandler.isActive
- Fixes ignored initial angle in mxRotationHandler
- Changes mxGraph.findTreeRoots to return List instead of Object[]
- Adds data:-prefix for embedded image short format
- Adds mxObjectCodec.getFieldTemplate, addObjectValue
- Moves mxModelCodec.encode to mxModelCodec.encodeObject
- Fixes gradients in mxLabelShape

22-NOV-2010: 1.5.0.0

- Adds mxGraph.postProcessCellStyle for resolving image keys
- Adds mxGraph.add/removeImageBundle, getImageFromBundles
- Adds mxGraph.imageBundles with accessors
- Adds mxImageBundle class for embedded images
- Adds support for data URIs in mxUtils.loadImage
- Removes unused constants in com.mxgraph.util.svg.CSSConstants
- Renames mxPngTextDecoder.decodezTXt to decodeCompressedText
- Renames mxPNGzTXtDecoder to mxPngTextDecoder
- Changes return type of mxGraphics2DCanvas.loadImage to BufferedImage
- Changes return type of mxUtils.loadImage to BufferedImage
- Fixes font sizes in printed output via mxGraphComponent.print
- Fixes mxGraphControl.extendComponent for negative coordinates

03-NOV-2010: 1.4.2.3

02-NOV-2010: 1.4.2.2

- Fixes handling of linefeeds in HTML labels with long text
- mxCellEditor replaces installKeyHandler with configureActionMaps
- mxCellEditor replaces key handler with input maps for key handling
- Adds mxCellEditor.extractHtmlBody, replaceLinefeeds, shiftEnterSubmitsText
- Moves mxGraphics2DCanvas.replaceHtmlLinefeeds to mxHtmlTextShape
- Fixes background rendering in image shapes
- Reduces unnecessary mxCurve re-calculations
- Fixes curve label character bounds
- Changes default colors, adds shapes in GraphEditor example
- Fixes default alignment for images in label shape
- Fixes size of images in mxLabelShape

22-OCT-2010: 1.4.2.1

19-OCT-2010: 1.4.2.0

- Improves edge routing in hierarchical layout
- Fixes in-place change of translate in mxBasicCanvas.setTranslate
- Adds mxMultiplicity.checkTerminal, checkNeighbors hooks

12-OCT-2010: 1.4.1.4

08-OCT-2010: 1.4.1.3

- Changes signature of mxConnectorShape.paintMarker
- Adds mxMarkerRegistry and pluggable markers

01-OCT-2010: 1.4.1.2

30-SEP-2010: 1.4.1.1

- Adds mxCodec.setDocument
- Changes various methods in the sharing package
- Deprecates changes parameter for change and notify events in mxGraphModel
- Adds edit parameter for change and notify event in mxGraphModel
- Wraps sequence of changes in  node in mxSession
- Adds accessors for fields in atomic changes for mxGraphModel
- Adds mxCodec.insertIntoGraph hook
- Ensures correct ordering of cells decoded in mxCodec
- mxUtils.getXml omits XML declaration

